data.text:
Media Condition : Near Mint (NM or M-)

Sleeve Condition: Very Good Plus (VG+)

Format : LP, Album, Mono

Genre : Jazz

Style : Bop

Label : Savoy Records

Country : US

Released: 1955

Notes:

Savoy Mono LP - silver/burgundy labels (not deep groove), laminated jacket.. Session originally recorded in 1953. Remastered for LP release by Van Gelder. Re-released in Japan in 1991.
